Author: Thomas Ruf, partially based on C original by Press et al. (Numerical Recipes) and the Python module Astropy.
Maintainer: Thomas Ruf <Thomas.Ruf@vetmeduni.ac.at>
Description: Computes the Lomb-Scargle Periodogram for unevenly sampled time series. Includes a randomization procedure to obtain exact p-values.
